Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.82,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,At the Hyatt Regency,\Nthe deadly change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.62,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,looked like a\Nshortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The walkway design\Nused one continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,hanger rod from roof\Nto fourth floor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.65,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,to second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In shop drawings, it\Nbecame two shorter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.24,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,rods, easier to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the load path\Nchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The fourth floor\Nconnection now carried both
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,walkways, not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.77,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The load essentially\Ndoubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:31.14,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,nbs later found the\Noriginal design was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:34.40,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,already weak the\Nrevision left roughly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.66,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,one-third of code\Nexpected capacity on july
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,17 1981 two walkways\Ncollapsed during a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:44.18,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,crowded dance official\Nrecords count 113
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:47.43,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,dead and 186 injured
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,This was not a shop\Ndetail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.21,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was a structural\Nredesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.26,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Every handoff treated\Nit like paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
